        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[建立一個 user:passwd 格式的檔案]]></title>
            <guid>6df249348cb245959ce15a273d28b4f2</guid>
            <pubDate>Thu, 27 Oct 2022 06:12:39 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>htpasswd 要的帳號密碼對應<br />
也可以拿來做其他用途</p>
<div><pre class="hljs"><code><span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">make</span> <span class="hljs-string">sure</span> <span class="hljs-string">/tmp/user_pass</span> <span class="hljs-string">exists</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">file:</span>
    <span class="hljs-attr">path:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/tmp/user_pass</span>
    <span class="hljs-attr">state:</span> <span class="hljs-string">touch</span>
  
<span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">register</span> <span class="hljs-string">previous</span> <span class="hljs-string">mapping</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">shell:</span> <span class="hljs-string">"cat /tmp/user_pass"</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">register:</span> <span class="hljs-string">"user_pass_reg"</span>
  
<span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">create</span> <span class="hljs-string">user/password</span> <span class="hljs-string">mapping</span> <span class="hljs-string">yml</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">lineinfile:</span> 
    <span class="hljs-attr">line:</span> <span class="hljs-string">"<span class="hljs-template-variable">{{ item.name }}</span>:<span class="hljs-template-variable">{{ lookup('ansible.builtin.password', '/dev/null length=8 chars=ascii_letters,digits') }}</span>"</span>
    <span class="hljs-attr">path:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/tmp/user_pass</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">with_items:</span> <span class="hljs-string">"<span class="hljs-template-variable">{{ users_nopassword }}</span>"</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">when:</span> <span class="hljs-string">not</span> <span class="hljs-string">user_pass_reg.stdout.find(item.name)</span> <span class="hljs-type">!=</span> <span class="hljs-number">-1</span></code></pre></div>
]]></content:encoded>
